Tar Examples

Tarring file
  tar -cvf filename.tar /home/user/filename.txt
 
Zipping Tarballs
  tar cvzf filename.tar.gz /home/user/filename.txt
  OR
  tar cvzf filename.tgz /home/user/filename.txt
  
 Extracting compressed tarballs
  tar -xvf filename.tar.gz
  OR
  tar -xvf filename.tar.gz -C /home/user/new location
